[ti:Movement II — Nunc Dimittis]
[ar:JiangJingyi]
[00:19.14]Now let your servant go in peace,||如今让您的仆人安息吧
[00:27.07]Your quiet word has brought release;||您轻柔的话语已带来解脱
[00:34.78]For these old eyes have seen the sign||因为这双老眼已见到那征兆
[00:41.33]That waited long beyond their time —||它在久远的岁月里等待——
[00:50.13]A small light cradled in our night,||在我们的黑夜中怀抱着一束微光
[00:57.24]A gentle dawn within our sight.||在我们的视野里迎来了一抹温柔的晨曦
[01:08.39]What now I hold is not a word,||此刻我拥有的并非言语
[01:16.05]Not shadow, not an echo heard,||非阴影，非耳畔回响
[01:22.53]But flesh and face and quiet breath,||而是血肉之躯，面容，轻柔的呼吸
[01:29.78]A warmth more lasting than our death.||一种比死亡更持久的温暖
[01:37.42]The ancient lamp was never lost,||那盏古灯从未遗失
[01:44.41]But kept through every night and frost;||历经无数寒夜霜雪
[01:51.61]The ancient promise, whispered low,||那句古老的低语诺言
[01:58.97]Wakes within this child I know.||唤醒了我所熟知的这孩子
[02:07.17]Light, you came into our night,||光明，你降临我们的黑夜
[02:14.69]Light, we kindled lamps so bright.||光明，我们点亮明灯如此明亮
[02:21.86]Light, you came to those you own,||光明，你来到你的子民身边
[02:28.36]You dwell in flesh, no more alone.||你居于肉身，不再孤单
[02:39.29]Now I may go, for I have seen,||如今我可以离去，因为我已得见
[02:46.57]Now I may rest, where hope has been;||如今我可以安息，在希望曾驻足之地
[02:54.03]A child has walked our mortal way…||一个孩子走过我们凡人的道路……
[03:03.27]Light… within these arms… stay…||光明……在这些臂弯里……留下……
[03:11.01]Light… within us… stay…||光明……在我们心中……留下……
[03:18.18]Light…||光明……
